{"word":"H4838 - מָרַק - mâraq - maw-rak' - Bright","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָרַק</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mâraq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>maw-rak'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bright"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துலக்கு, சுத்தமாயிரு, கழுவப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to scour, to polish"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to scour, to polish"},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual) to be scoured"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>polish</i>; by implication to <i>sharpen</i>; also to <i>rinse: - </i>bright, furbish, scour."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4795 - מָרוּק - mârûwq - maw-rook'/4795\">H4795</a>, <a href=\"#/H4838 - מָרַק - mâraq - maw-rak'/4838\">H4838</a>, <a href=\"#/H8562 - תַּמְרוּק - tamrûwq - tam-rook'/8562\">H8562</a>"}]}